reviewText: Great value with fast and free shipping...  +++++
Dudes! This is a great series that's wacky and erotically charged. #2 is my favorite--you know what I mean!--It has balls! <g> Sometimes campy, but always entertaining. I highly recommend it!
I thought these were really funny moveies, I have whatched them several times. I how ever would not recomend them for a minor or unmature person.
